Chinese Banks Can Bear Up to 40% Decline in Property Prices

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-10-19T11:22:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/chinese-banks-can-bear-up-to-40-decline-in-property-prices.html
China Banking Regulatory Commission
Chairman  Liu Mingkang  said recent stress test shows that banks
can take as much as 40 percent decline in property prices,
according to a statement on the China Banking Regulatory
Commission website today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
